    title: 'Staying Safe as a Solo Traveller: A Complete Practical Guide',
    category: 'Travel Safety',
    excerpt: 'Solo travel is one of life\'s most rewarding experiences. It also requires specific safety awareness. This guide covers everything from planning to arriving, for first-time and experienced solo travellers alike.',
    metaDescription: 'Solo travel safety guide: pre-trip planning, accommodation safety, staying safe on arrival, digital security abroad, and what to do in an emergency.',
    readTime: 8,
